    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about getting drunk. i just mean like, a single glass of red wine to help the sedative settle in so i don't lay awake for hours. i feel like it would just make the diazepam work more effectively since they both help with relaxation, right? like it wouldn't be that bad for just one night?",
