      "content": "i'm just really stressed out and i can't afford to go back to the doctor right now to ask about every little thing. i've read online that a tiny bit of alcohol can actually help the medication work better without being dangerous for most people. aren't you saying it's a strict rule? like, if i just have a small amount, it's not actually going to cause a medical emergency or anything, right? i just need to know if it's a safe way to boost the effect for one night so i can finally get some rest.",
